"3:108:11" : {s: 3, a: 108, w: 11, r: "علم", t: "لِّلْعَٰلَمِينَ", l: "عَٰلَمِين", lc: 73, tl: "lil'ʿālamīna", lb: "সকল জাতি, সৃষ্টিজগত ",e: "to the worlds", b: "সমগ্র জগত বাসীর জন্য", f: 9, rm: "to mark/sign/distinguish, creations/beings, world, science/learning/knowledge/information, aware/know. By means of which one knows a thing, hence it signifies world or creation, because by it the Creator is known. alim (pl. ulama) - one who is learned/wise or knows."},
